After the user approves the direction, save the brief to:

```bash
mkdir -p ~/.gstack/projects/$SLUG
TS=$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S)
echo "$TS"
```

Write the approved brief to:
- `~/.gstack/projects/$SLUG/${TS}-product-iteration.md`

Then tell the user:
- where the brief was saved
- which direction you recommend testing first
- whether `/plan-ceo-review` should be run next on the chosen direction

